The primary visual proof of this study is the _Ablation Wall_, rendered in Phase 2: Model Evidence of the Deal Intelligence Terminal. It plots AUC-ROC across four algorithm families — Logistic Regression, XGBoost (Untuned), XGBoost (Tuned), and MLP — for the M1 (Financial Only) and M3 (Financial + Text + Graph) configurations, with ±1σ cross-validation error bars on every bar. @tbl-ablation reproduces the headline figures.

